        public R timeOut​(java.time.Duration timeOut)
        This method defines the time to wait for the value is absent.

        WARNING!

        When there is a function that is used to find a value to be absent and it was received by invocation of SequentialGetStepSupplier.get() and there is a timeout defined by SequentialGetStepSupplier.timeOut(Duration) then this timeout is ignored in favor of the time value defined by timeOut(Duration)
